Comment: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:41.35,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.22,0:00:21.12,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Touka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:22.98,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Buď trpezlivá.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:24.11,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:26.82,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale čakanie je také...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:34.64,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako je Oborovi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:40.23,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Občas má nočné mory, ale to je asi tak všetko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:41.17,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:42.59,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.82,0:00:44.13,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Vôbec o tom nehovorí...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:46.33,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa vlastne stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:46.78,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:48.56,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.80,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak... bol ťažko ranený!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:00:57.69,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:01:00.42,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol ťažko ranený.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:06.95,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimochodom, čo je s Toukou?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:09.47,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? S Toukou niečo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:12.85,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerá, ako by ju trápila nejaká choroba.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:15.40,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:30.21,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ale, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:34.33,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nemyslel som si, že by mohla byť taká smutná kvôli bábke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:40.37,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A tento zvuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:42.60,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Je to ako prekliatie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:46.16,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nedokážem zaspať, ak ho budem musieť počúvať.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:55.26,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Počul som, že toto je najlepší opravár hračiek v krajine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.33,0:01:56.93,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Takže sme tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:01.80,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáčte za zdržanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:02.79,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.71,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Pane! Pane!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:12.70,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozrite sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:14.66,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Moja bábika je opravená.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:17.52,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Už je to dlho, čo som urobil tak dobrú prácu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.73,0:02:19.39,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, dajte na ňu pozor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:20.39,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:22.30,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Veľakrát vám ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:27.80,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, tu máte.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:31.63,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Pane, opravu som chcela zaplatiť ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:32.78,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Zamietam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:34.99,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Robím to pre teba, tak sa netráp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:37.65,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Pane...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.94,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy vám to nezabudnem, nikdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:42.60,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, nie,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:44.56,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,nezaťažuj sa tým.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.48,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Niečo také nehovorte.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.57,0:02:52.61,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,To je vecou cti, splatiť pánovi jeho láskavosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:02.36,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz...som ako podvodník.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:06.30,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Vitajte, vitajte! Vyprážané mororo. Ešte sú teplé!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.92,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo keby sme si zajedli?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:11.72,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Máte pravdu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:15.18,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak ja zaplatím jedlo ako poďakovanie za opravenie bábiky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:16.69,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím počkajte tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.06,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Dva krát, prosím.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:20.95,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, hneď.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:29.29,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nemá peňaženku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:42.22,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhnite! Chceme prejsť! Ponáhľame sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:56.58,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkajte!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:57.93,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Touka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:03.86,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Snáď ich nechce dobehnúť?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:06.49,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Um.... to by bola hlúposť.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:09.38,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Nezastavia sa dokým neprídu do susednej krajiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:19.85,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kashirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:20.50,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:21.79,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Žena.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:26.16,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Nejaká žena nás prenasleduje, pešo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.35,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Hlupák!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:30.42,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Ľudské nohy nevyvinú takúto rýchlosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.54,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Netrep hlúposti a pozeraj dopredu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:33.82,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.35,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,To...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:37.18,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Že ťa to ešte baví...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:38.47,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,vymýšľať také vtipy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:45.09,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Čakajte...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:49.14,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Vráťte mi ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:53.04,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Pridaj, pridaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:56.65,utaware alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Čakajte, čakajte!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.69,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Čakajte!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:02.46,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, vráťte mi ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.46,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Vráťte mi ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:08.72,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Vráťte mi ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:21.95,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuoro, tvoj čaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:23.95,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:28.74,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimochodom, ako je Touke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:30.25,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, áno,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:32.92,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,občas má nočné mory,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:35.52,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,ale teraz je už jej lepšie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:39.39,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Muselo to byť pre ňu ťažké, čo sa vlastne stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.90,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:46.71,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Po desiatich dňoch sa vrátila aj s bábkou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:50.64,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Musela to mať naozaj ťažké.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:53.97,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zaujímalo by ma, kam ich až prenasledovala.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:56.52,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:59.70,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,počula som zvesti o bohu Nugizono.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:01.03,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Počul si ich tiež?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:02.74,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Boh Nugizono?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:05.73,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Boh, ktorý sa mení na ženu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.95,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Beží rýchlejšie ako kôň,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.55,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,a je horšia ako Kimama.\N{\i1}(Kimama - jeden z zlých bohov)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:17.76,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Má hrôzostrašný výraz a neupravené vlasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.45,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,A jej hlas je ako ozvena z pekla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:24.34,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,"Vráťte mi ho!" kričala po svojich obetiach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:27.97,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Vráťte mi ho--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:30.23,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy sa nevzdialila nech utekali akokoľvek dlho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:34.57,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak po nej začali hádzať veci aby ju zastavili.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.69,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale aj tak ich stále prenasledovala.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:40.82,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,"Už tu nič nie je!",
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:45.08,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,kričali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:46.90,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,A ona potom povedala,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:50.41,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tak si zoberiem vaše životy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:58.08,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovorím pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.67,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj sa to dvom ľuďom stalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:04.29,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak je to pravda, ako vyviazli?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:07.20,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Je tu jedna možnosť ako sa zachrániť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.98,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Jedna možnosť?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:09.75,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.69,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Bábika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:12.84,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Bábika?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.53,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak sa vyhodí bábika,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.53,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,zmýli si ju s človekom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:20.32,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,A potom ju začne jesť od hlavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:42.17,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Zatiaľ čo jedla tak stihli ujsť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:48.14,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Tí ľudia hovorili, že ich tá bábika zachránila.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:49.72,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Bábika?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:51.84,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,To snáď...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:04.12,utaware def,,0000,0000,0000,,Zvládla som to...
